            "note": "Tapping into the enormous potential of conducting meta-analyses on the ever increasing number of metabolomics studies requires structured metadata annotation to allow for a meaningful dataset integration and prepare data-mining analysis. XemlLab is a GUI-assisted metadata capture workflow enabling the intuitive design of experiments and management of environmental data. We rely on environmental, structural and developmental stage ontologies for controlled vocabularies. Moreover XemlLab is desined to be integrated with experimental data repositories and exporting datasets to databases is easy.",
